title: Hawkeye 01-22 (2012) (Complete Series) (theProletariat-Novus)
description:
This torrent includes the entire 22 issue run of what many consider to be THE Hawkeye series to read, period.  Three versions are provided: HD (2048px) without ads, c2c (mix of HD and SD), and noAds (SD).
*Note: I've organized this torrent with a top-level separation between hd, c2c and noAds versions.  This makes it super easy for you to just choose one folder or the other depending on whether you want all hd, c2c or noAds.  There is also a separate folder for additional printing variant covers, provided by ScanDog.
========================================================

Thanks goes to theProletariat and ZeroDaze for these releases, and ScanDog for all of the wonderful variant covers
